This silver lockpick twists and reorients itself to more easily open locks. Gain an [[advantage]] when you attempt to pick a lock with this tool. As a [[consequence]] of a [[bad outcome]], the pick might cast the [[knock]] spell on the lock before the pick turns to dust and is destroyed.